Step-1
create a vulome in aws with in same region (cluster, and vulome are same region)
- aws vulome
- create a vulome (100gb)

Step-2
Install ebs drivers in terminal 
- first the kubectl version
-  kubectl apply -k "github.com/kubernetes-sigs/aws-ebs-csi-driver/deploy/kubernetes/overlays/stable/?ref=release-1.29"
-  kubectl get pods -n kube-system | grep ebs # check the ebs drivers are install or not
-